The first thing is to ensure the house is as fully restored as possible and kept in good order. Membership of the Historic Houses organisation, and funding from{English Heritage}has been a great help at Burton Constable.
Next, a full use of all resources. The grounds are fully farmed, and are also developing as a Country Park, with a {caravan site, camping, fishing, {boating}and in the stable blocks{model {railways, refreshments and motorcycle, {carriage and agricultural museums.}In the Hall are{furniture trails}and a fine collection of{Georgian scientific {instruments.}
School parties visit and weekends are held for{crafts, antiques, traction {engine and light aircraft rallies}and the newer sport of{microliting.}
